# Newsletter capture — Buttondown
#
# Get your API key at https://buttondown.com/settings/api (Settings → API).
# When this is set, POST /api/subscribe forwards signups to Buttondown.
# When unset (e.g. local dev), signups fall back to data/subscribers.json.
#
# On Vercel: add this in Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# (do NOT commit a real key — copy this file to .env.local for local use).
BUTTONDOWN_API_KEY=
